Check out these fall off the bone ribs we smoked on our @grillagrills Silverbac AT! This all terrain  wood pellet smoker creates perfectly smoked meat, bursting with juice and smokey flavor!

For the ribs, we used BBQ brown sugar coating and cooked them on low for 5.5-6 hours. Recipe to be uploaded soon! 
Musician: Jef
Song: King

#grillagrill #silverbacat

Squid Ink Fettuccini served at Calypzo, @hyattzilarajm’s beachfront grill house.

🎥:@restauranteating
